Interface ClusterDiscoveryService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalClusterDiscoveryService

    public interface ClusterDiscoveryService
    Abstraction for service that keeps track of clusters. These clusters are normally stored in a some naming service. The implementation handles any custom exclusions.
